            "title": "A New Species of Chigger (Acari: Trombiculidae) from Indonesia and Current Differentiation of Trombicula Berlese, 1905 Sensu Stricto Group",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Stanislav",
                    "lastName": "Kalúz"
                },
